## COMMANDS

### copy

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] fs copy
  *config-filter-name* *source-path* *dest-path*

**doveadm** [*GLOBAL OPTIONS*] mail fs copy
  [**-u** *user* | **-F** *file*]
